{"tid":1685412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認真，點樣申請禁制令？","createTime":"2019-10-31T13:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T05:30:57.000Z","uid":267103,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e667c1840825262d1c7cdb85f7e8b9fb6e5ef333","tid":1685412,"uid":267103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:53:05.000Z","msg":"作為一名香港市民，<br />\n對香港警察由六月至今刻意隱藏身分、拒絕向市民出示委任證、蒙面濫權執法的所有惡行感到相當不齒及憤怒。而律政司多次極速批出禁制令，損害香港人自由和權利，更遑論有好好維持香港的法治，真令人感到唏噓。<br />\n<br />\n入正題：<br />\n六月曾有人申請禁制令，<br />\n但已無下文。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OaBjKda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOaBjKda.jpg&h=84419f0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n查過資料但都係唔太明申請禁制令既方法。<br />\n大家可以指教下？<br />\n關於警察牠們並無遵守相關警察通例，又係咪可以作為申請既理據？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uLVsS6W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuLVsS6W.jpg&h=f828f472&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JAM7S6X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJAM7S6X.jpg&h=807d557d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ha2fhyC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHa2fhyC.jpg&h=8d6a5e20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n謝謝大家。<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可"},{"pid":"4bc92b6691b0089e1b99882c3a569a8a7070ab55","tid":1685412,"uid":277273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u7gjKeN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu7gjKeN.png&h=9eed29c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76e64afcbc0912bd742472cbebf11c84a7544fc0","tid":1685412,"uid":170185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:55:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3a3592f2917c454cd5d07d67f4bd41aab5dcad3","tid":1685412,"uid":185057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:59:19.000Z","msg":"去法政匯思問下會唔會有解答?"},{"pid":"6754678dfeb